**ttak_tam_tam**
- [ maṭal ]
s. anything that is flat and long as the leaves of the cocoa
palmyra
plantain etc.
2. eyelid
நிமை;
3. a flowerpetal
பூவிதழ்;
4. the shoulder blade and upper arm
தோள்மடல்;
5. a stand for sacred ashes
விபூதி மடல்;
6. a poem figuratively describing a disappointed lover riding on a palmyrastem
[ mṭl ]
s. any thing flat and long
espe cially the leaves of the cocoa
areka
plantain
screwpine (தாழை) and wild date
phoe; nix farinifera
ஈந்துமுதலியவற் றின்ஏடு
2. a stand for sacred ashes. பார். திருநீற்றுமடல்
